---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="Frequently Asked Questions - PNW Technology Solutions">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection 
      title="Frequently Asked Questions" 
      highlightText="Questions"
      description="Find answers to common questions about PNW Technology Solutions and our web development services."
    />
    
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <!-- FAQ Categories Navigation -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
            <a href="#general" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-primary-200 dark:hover:bg-primary-800 transition-colors">
              General
            </a>
            <a href="#services" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors">
              Services & Pricing
            </a>
            <a href="#process" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors">
              Process
            </a>
            <a href="#technical" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors">
              Technical
            </a>
            <a href="#support" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors">
              Support
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <!-- General FAQs -->
          <div id="general" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 16h-1v-4h-1m1-4h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              General Questions
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What is PNW Technology Solutions?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  PNW Technology Solutions is a web development consultancy that brings proven open source technologies to small business owners and artists. We specialize in WordPress customization, modern web development with React and Astro, and helping the little people build professional websites without enterprise price tags.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Who do you work with?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We specialize in helping small businesses, artists, and solo entrepreneurs who need professional websites but don't have enterprise budgets. This includes local restaurants, freelance consultants, photographers, musicians, Etsy shop owners, and service providers who want to compete online.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What makes you different from other web developers?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We focus exclusively on bringing enterprise-grade open source technologies to small businesses at affordable rates. We charge $50/hour for quick updates, provide honest pricing upfront, and use proven technologies instead of experimental solutions. You work directly with us, not junior developers or outsourced teams.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you only work with clients in the Pacific Northwest?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  While we're based in the Pacific Northwest, we work with small businesses and artists anywhere. All our services can be delivered remotely, and we're experienced at collaborating with clients across different time zones.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Services & Pricing FAQs -->
          <div id="services" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Services & Pricing
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What services do you offer?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We offer three main services: Quick Updates ($50/hour) for small changes to existing WordPress or Squarespace sites, Custom Development (custom quotes) for new websites and complex projects, and Consultation ($75/hour) for strategic guidance on technology choices and digital planning. Visit our <a href="/pricing" class="text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 hover:underline">pricing page</a> for detailed information.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How much does a new website cost?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Custom development pricing varies based on your specific needs, complexity, and timeline. Simple business websites typically start around $2,000-5,000, while more complex e-commerce or custom applications can range higher. We provide detailed quotes after understanding your requirements during our free 15-minute consultation.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you offer payment plans?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes, we understand that small businesses need flexible payment options. For larger projects, we typically structure payments as 50% upfront and 50% upon completion. For very large projects, we can discuss milestone-based payment plans to spread costs over time.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you offer ongoing maintenance?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Absolutely! Many clients use our $50/hour Quick Updates service for ongoing maintenance, content updates, and small improvements. We don't lock you into monthly contracts - you only pay for the time you actually use.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Process FAQs -->
          <div id="process" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Process
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How do we get started?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Every project starts with a free 15-minute consultation where we listen to your needs and explain how we can help - no sales pitch, just honest advice. If it's a good fit, we'll provide a clear quote and timeline. For quick updates, we can often start work the same day.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How long does a typical project take?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Quick updates are usually completed within 1-3 business days. Simple business websites typically take 2-4 weeks, while more complex projects with e-commerce or custom functionality can take 6-12 weeks. We'll give you a realistic timeline during the quote process.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What do I need to provide?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  To get started, we just need access to your current website (if you have one), a clear idea of what you want to achieve, and any specific content or branding guidelines. Don't worry if you're not sure - we can help clarify your needs during the consultation.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Will my website be mobile-friendly?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Absolutely! All websites we develop are fully responsive and mobile-friendly, ensuring they look great and function well on all devices. We can provide specific mobile design samples upon request.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Technical FAQs -->
          <div id="technical" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 9c0 5.591 3.824 10.29 9 11.622 5.176-1.332 9-6.03 9-11.622 0-1.042-.133-2.052-.382-3.016z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Technical
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What platform do you use for web development?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We primarily use WordPress for content-driven websites, and React or Astro for modern, interactive web applications. These platforms allow us to deliver high-quality, scalable, and maintainable websites. We can also work with other platforms if required.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How do you ensure website quality?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Quality is ensured through rigorous testing, code reviews, and adherence to best practices in web development. We test websites on multiple devices and browsers to ensure compatibility and performance. Our goal is to deliver a website that not only meets but exceeds your expectations.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Can you help with website hosting and domain registration?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes, we can assist with website hosting and domain registration as part of our services. We recommend reliable and secure hosting providers and can manage the setup and migration of your website to the new host. We also offer ongoing maintenance and support for your hosting environment.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What if I need changes after the website is live?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We offer flexible post-launch support and maintenance options. You can request changes or updates at any time, and we'll provide a quote based on the scope of work. Many clients opt for our Quick Updates service for ongoing changes and improvements.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Support FAQs -->
          <div id="support" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Support
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What kind of support does PNW Technology Solutions offer?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We offer multiple support channels to ensure you get the help you need when you need it. All plans include email support with a 24-hour response time. Professional and Enterprise plans also include live chat support during business hours, and Enterprise plans include dedicated phone support and a named account manager.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you offer training and onboarding assistance?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes, we provide comprehensive onboarding assistance for all customers. Professional and Enterprise plans include personalized onboarding sessions with our customer success team. We also offer a rich library of documentation, video tutorials, and webinars to help you get the most out of Sassify.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Is there a community forum for Sassify users?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes, we have an active community forum where users can share tips, ask questions, and connect with other Sassify users. Our team also participates in the forum to provide guidance and collect feedback. It's a great resource for learning best practices and staying up-to-date with the latest features.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How can I request a new feature?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We welcome feature requests and value your input! You can submit feature requests through our customer portal, community forum, or by contacting our support team. We regularly review and prioritize feature requests based on customer demand and strategic alignment.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center mt-16">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Still have questions?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
              Our team is here to help. Contact us and we'll get back to you as soon as possible.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Contact Support</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>

